{"type":"message","id":"4250cf5f","parentId":"8acca0cc","timestamp":"2026-03-16T13:53:16.736Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see there are actually 3 agents:1. main - Main Agent\n2. agent_admin - Agent Admin\n3. interview-agent - 面试助手\n\nBut the issue is that when the user chats, they can only use main agent. This is likely because:\n1. The other agents (agent_admin and interview-agent) are not configured in the `agents.list` in openclaw.json - they're loaded from the agents directory but not explicitly registered\n2. There's no routing rules to direct messages to different agents\n\nThe user wants to be able to use other agents in their chat. Let me check the current config and add routing rules or add them to the list properly.","thinkingSignature":"2b6324f5fc3212f808cc9413d267e190f492f20aec76ccd942a3a4fe6c56ccca"},{"type":"text","text":"确实有 3 个 agent，但它们没有在配置中正确注册。让我检查并修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u4kgtz08akn3_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":96051,"output":195,"cacheRead":36917,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133163,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773669183783}}
